241;TRIM-GT-1341/2017;04/12/2017 16:00;Supervisor;DRG;;;IRB;;Todos os Segmentos;Em Produção;Deficiência de Processo;13;The institution does not present a structured process to perform the quantitative impact assessment.;;The institution should use transparent definitions and clear internal procedures in order to perform the quantitative impact assessment according to the Commission Delegated Regulation (EU) no. 529/2014. In particular, this process should be completely clear on the sample of data and key assumptions used to produce the impact assessment.;;;;;;;;Risco Médio;30/12/2018 16:00;Final;;Concluída;;The improved process as described in the previous section will be documented in the internal document “Gestão de Alterações e Extensões ao método IRB – Definição de Procedimentos e Governance” until 30 June 2018.;30/06/2018;Documento “Gestão de Alterações e Extensões ao método IRB – Definição de Procedimentos e Governance”;30/06/2022 06:17;19/09/2024 08:34;Item;sites/ComitdeModelos/Lists/Findings Followup CMA v20;;;;;;
